Package it.polimi.ingsw

Class Controller

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.controller.Controller
All Implemented Interfaces:
ProxyObserver
public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProxyObserver
This class implements the controller of the server. It's notified by ServerView and manages the match, it chooses which action every player needs to make, it reacts to the players' actions by checking if they are correct and consequently it modifies the game model.

The initialization procedure follows this order:

  • onInitialization()
  • onGodPowerInitialization(int playerId, String godPower): called for each player
  • onWorkerPositionsInitialization()
  • onWorkerPositionsInitialization(int playerId, List workerPositions): called for each player

After the initialization procedure nextOperation() is called.
